headline: Warner Bros. Discovery President and CEO David Zaslav to Present at the Morgan Stanley 2025 Technology, Media & Telecom Conference
summary: Warner Bros. Discovery, Inc. (Nasdaq: WBD) today announced that its President and CEO David Zaslav will present at Morgan Stanley's 2025 Technology, Media & Telecom Conference on Tuesday, March 4, 2025 at 10:00 a.m. ET (7:00 a.m. PT).
